</table>
<p><b>Hausa</b> is the <a href="/wiki/Chadic_languages" title="Chadic languages">Chadic language</a> with the largest number of speakers, spoken as a first <a href="/wiki/Language" title="Language">language</a> by about 25 million people, and as a second language by about 18 million more.<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
